Columns:

*   ticker
*   date
*   path\_to\_intraday
*   number\_of\_samples
*   gap\_pct
*   float
*   news\_flag
*   etc.

This lets you:

*   shuffle across tickers
*   build training/validation splits
*   avoid data leakage

